(define-fun is-power-of-two ((x (_ BitVec 4))) Bool 
  (= #x0 (bvand x (bvsub x #x1))))
(declare-const a (_ BitVec 4))
(assert 
 (not (= (is-power-of-two a) 
         (or (= a #x0) 
             (= a #x1) 
             (= a #x2) 
             (= a #x4) 
             (= a #x8)))))
(check-sat)
